{"tid":1519151,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［想潑好耐嘅冷水］香港抗爭屢戰屢敗嘅原因","createTime":"2019-08-30T13:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:11:34.000Z","uid":173326,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c2370f57ca9958df16a049ce1cd9cbbdf67b1937","tid":1519151,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"好多港豬想要民主自由，但少少險都唔想冒，連聽日出街行街都唔敢。<br />\n<br />\n一個二個只等其他人流血、被捕、犧牲，自己食住花生坐享其成，會奮不顧身救人嘅只係少數。<br />\n<br />\n大家都做見證勝利嘅人，而唔係做建立勝利嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭人上下一心，個個唔怕死去抗爭、去救人;<br />\n香港人大部分只會嗌口號、嘉年華式抗爭，得少數人真係將個人榮辱放低。<br />\n<br />\n好多人同強國人一樣咁自私、唔團結，只想坐享其成，所以強國、香港嘅抗爭從來冇成功過。<br />\n<br />\n希望睇到呢到，各位可以鼓起勇氣去聽日嘅831、行動上再踏出一步。"},{"pid":"0743244d305d502e5653fe3ebb945b9bf5dfaed9","tid":1519151,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0oeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=ec884a8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0oeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=85881f27\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0oeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=7288f2e2\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4678f4698a20e97efa5944d77aaa79d89c056d33","tid":1519151,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"